{"tid":1533020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中秋多人，係出動嘅最佳時機；亦請全民黑衫落街慶節，等狗狗冇得返屋企過節","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:08:57.000Z","uid":44751,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"18033038382464ef2e3eb0b9f2754450a182d342","tid":1533020,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"Hit and Run，行動完入去啲多人聚嘅公園<br />\n換好左衫，你就係落街玩嘅人<br />\n<br />\n個日入大廈都冇咁難，帶住月餅、碌柚，去探親戚啦喂，係保安個關先除口罩，之後再戴返<br />\n<br />\n唔使做啲乜野大事，塞鎖匙窿、紅油、塞爆信箱、麻包袋，你自己諗<br />\n唔一定搞黑狗，插爆信報女記肺刀手、機場蝦女仔保安、太子拉住手足嘅海關、八婆幼稚園老師，總有一個住你個區附近<br />\n<br />\n請大家係自己區嘅公海同grp，keep住提手足做野，或者將老豆搵到嘅同區仔資料，日日forward過去，啲人咁猖狂，就係知俾你地搵到都冇後果呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n叫曬你地老豆老母、舊同學落街玩通宵，要條街好多好多黑衫人<br />\n<br />\n記住，越多人做野就越安全，念力無法救港，自由都唔係係天跌落黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地場仗一輸，被捕手足終將淪為condom</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzHOaHu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzHOaHu.png&h=10971f79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Dadfindboy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDadfindboy&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=e29bfb04\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Dadfindboy</a>"},{"pid":"3638f44d197e71b8af835af0ce1e794cef870f7c","tid":1533020,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:00:40.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"a886b8a956c9d1927459b4cb8903cb0a24eaf4cc","tid":1533020,"uid":258669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"封狗屋.."},{"pid":"8e02ea055bfe283ea06c623b67475c3019673e1a","tid":1533020,"uid":44751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"話見保安除罩唔係撚化大家，純粹係驚個保安見你戴口罩，放你入去但又報警，大家可自行諗個安全方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但入𨋢一定要遮樣！！！</span>"},{"pid":"82a3e7cbdc725d6b3ac1361b70724d0daf20b48d","tid":1533020,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a886b8a956c9d1927459b4cb8903cb0a24eaf4cc","tid":1533020,"uid":258669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"封狗屋.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"一人一個單車鎖鎖閂點睇？"},{"pid":"9b086694051d37b245f9fe7b6d385e6ea96fce32","tid":1533020,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82a3e7cbdc725d6b3ac1361b70724d0daf20b48d","tid":1533020,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a886b8a956c9d1927459b4cb8903cb0a24eaf4cc","tid":1533020,"uid":258669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"封狗屋.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"一人一個單車鎖鎖閂點睇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"好似個啲情侶熱門打卡勝地咁，有好多同心鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4b337fee6897649cbdbf1dd06fd017e3658e26","tid":1533020,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bacaf664488b77d072ac3cf47b2d41961e7181cc","tid":1533020,"uid":44751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鎖完狗屋就即刻走，呢啲先係真快閃</span><br />\n<br />\n繼續集思廣益<br />\n我睇佢地保得住啲家人同藍絲，定係自己狗屋！"},{"pid":"db32bdbcf4ac74af79415511de5392d947f81fea","tid":1533020,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [國難老闆同一眾員工已保釋,開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1